## 默认环境变量配置（直接使用local环境配置）
# 使用全局环境配置文件 http-client.env.json
# 请在IntelliJ IDEA中选择对应环境: local/dev/test/gateway
# 登录成功后会自动更新token到环境变量中

### 1. 获取今日违规统计信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/security-risk-monitoring/today-violation-summary
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: 184717008866115584

### 2. 获取今日地址违规TOP5
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/security-risk-monitoring/violation-address-top5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 3. 获取违规数据趋势
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/security-risk-monitoring/violation-trend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 4. 获取违规分布
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/security-risk-monitoring/violation-distribution
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 5. 获取当前摄像机截屏列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/tiangong/security-risk-monitoring/camera-screenshot-list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}